		<title>Daily Market Snapshot: Employment Data Underwhelms, Stocks Fall, Yields Drop</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/en-au/analysis/market-snapshot/daily-market-snapshot-9-september-2024</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nick Twidale - ATFX Chief Market Analyst]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 23:14:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Market Snapshot]]></category>
