		<title>Daily Market Snapshot: US Employment Data in Focus</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/en-au/analysis/market-snapshot/daily-market-snapshot-6-september-2024</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nick Twidale - ATFX Chief Market Analyst]]></dc:creator>
