		<title>Daily Market Snapshot: US Markets Move Lower on Disappointing Jobs Data</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/en-au/analysis/market-snapshot/daily-market-snapshot-5-september-2024</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nick Twidale - ATFX Chief Market Analyst]]></dc:creator>
